data.title: What's the Name of the Film? (2022)
data.meta_description: What's the Name of the Film?: Directed by Pinar Fontini. What's the Name of the Film? is on the 68 generation of women filmmakers who made their films in 1990s Turkey. Following their journeys, the film depicts the socio-political panorama of Turkey's last 60 years in its background.
